snippet.title: This Is Not Your House - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist the game on Steam - THIS IS NOT YOUR HOUSE

Follow the developer on Twitter\X - eyes_trash

Follow the Composer on Instagram - jamison_miles_jackson

Game will release on itch.io & Steam on August 23, 2024

This Is Not Your House is a 2-bit Psychological Horror Choose Your Own Adventure game where you can crush someone's skull, suffer from hypothermia, transcend your mortal frame, and find all 10 unique endings. 


#indie #indiegame #indiegames #indiedev #visualnovel #horrorgaming #chooseyourownadventure #retro #retrogaming #retrogames #2bit
